        "subject": "LU-6025 utils: reset optind before calls to getopt_long()",
        "message": "LU-6025 utils: reset optind before calls to getopt_long()\n\nThe nodemap commands in lctl were not properly resetting optind\nbetween calls to getopt_long(). This patch sets optind to 0 before\ncalling any subcommands.\n\nThis patch is back-ported from the following one:\nLustre-commit: 81b3399d79d6e8bbe64d3fb68c27209274b4cf9c\nLustre-change: http://review.whamcloud.com/13063\n\nSigned-off-by: Kit Westneat <kit.westneat@gmail.com>\nChange-Id: I2a8c39ec4439cba8ce43bdab8807a374818c1197\n"
